Prokaryotic Virus Orthologous Groups

VOG Table - Description of all virus orthologous groups and their mapping to POGs 2013.

* NOTE: When the column "Protein Annotations" in this table shows "No annotation provided", this means that no annotation was present for protein sequences retrieved from some genomes in NCBI Nucleotide in May 2016.
* NOTE: The following search box is a "contains character" rather than an "exact match" tool. For instance, 1. searching for "150" in the Mapping column would match both "POG0150" and "POG1150"; 2. a search for “v pro” will return "v protein" and also “putative protein”
* NOTE: “VOG number” column sorts alphabetically rather than numerically (i.e., VOGs with numbers > 10,000 show up before 9999).
